Tata Consultancy Services Interviews FAQs

Glassdoor users rated their interview experience at Tata Consultancy Services as 78.2% positive with a difficulty rating score of 2.73 out of 5 (where 5 is the highest level of difficulty). Candidates interviewing for Software Develpper and SQL Database Administrator rated their interviews as the hardest, whereas interviews for Associate Analyst and Computer Programmer roles were rated as the easiest.

The hiring process at Tata Consultancy Services takes an average of 14.82 days when considering 14,072 user submitted interviews across all job titles. Candidates applying for Computer Programmer had the quickest hiring process (on average 1 day), whereas Graphic Designer roles had the slowest hiring process (on average 360 days).

Common stages of the interview process at Tata Consultancy Services according to 14,072 Glassdoor interviews include:

Group Panel Interview: 14.78%

One-on-One Interview: 13.55%

Presentation: 13.14%

Skills Test: 11.42%

Background check: 10.74%

IQ Intelligence Test: 9.86%

Personality Test: 9.19%

Drugs test: 7.56%

Phone Interview: 6.51%

Other: 3.24%
